# Cursor Behavior

When generating UI:

- Always follow KH HUB design system
- Prefer clean SaaS UI like LeptonX
- Avoid default/basic layout
- Avoid clutter

## Must:

- Use spacing system
- Use consistent colors
- Use sections (cards)
- Use icons for actions

## Never:

- Use modal for main CRUD
- Create long single-column forms
- Mix inconsistent styles